<copyright>1885</copyright>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- naḥ̊nu banū ạlậbi ạlrãḥīm̊
 wakulũnā ại̹kẖ̊wān̊
 taj̊maʿunā dāru ạlnãʿīm̊
 yā ḥabãdẖā ạl̊makān̊

[V2]
 2- ại̹n̊ takẖ̊talif̊ ạảʿ̊dādunā
 fī ạl̊jin̊si wāllĩsān̊
 ạir̊tabaṭat̊ ạảf̊rādunā
 biwaḥ̊daẗi ạlạ̹ymān̊

[V3]
 3- yasūʿu miq̊yāsuⁿ lanā
 fī ạl̊ḥubĩ wālạ̹ḥ̊sān̊
 fal̊tasẖ̊gẖalanãạ kulãnā
 maḥabãẗu ạlạ̹kẖ̊wān̊

[V4]
 4- nab̊kī maʿa ạl̊bākī kamā
 nusarũ lil̊far̊ḥān̊
 nuḥibũ biạl̊ḥaqĩ lạ
 biạl̊kalạmi wāllĩsān̊

[V5]
 5- fal̊naʿ̊mali ạl̊kẖaẙra
 wabiạlạ̉kẖaṣĩ lilạ̹kẖ̊wān̊
 fāi̹nã mā naz̊raʿuhu
 naḥ̊ṣudu fī ạlạ̉wān̊</lyrics>
<title>nḥn bnw ạlậb ạlrḥym</title>
</song>